# Channel Geometry

## Overview

This folder contains data and analyses related to channel geometry with a focus on river bends. It includes various files and subfolders necessary for understanding and analyzing the morphological changes in river planforms over time.

## Reference

When using or referring to the data and analyses in this folder, please cite the following paper:

Schwenk, J., Khandelwal, A., Fratkin, M., Kumar, V., & FoufoulaGeorgiou, E. (2017). High spatiotemporal resolution of river planform dynamics from Landsat: The RivMAP toolbox and results from the Ucayali River. Earth Space Sci., 4, 46â€“75. This paper provides foundational methodology and insights that were instrumental in the analyses performed on the datasets contained within this directory.
